'''Bulgartransgaz EAD''' is a natural gas transmission and storage system operator of [[Bulgaria]]. It is a subsidiary of [[Bulgarian Energy Holding EAD]].<ref name=sofia190908> {{cite news | url = http://sofiaecho.com/2008/09/19/663793_bulgaria-merges-energy-firms-in-4b-euro-holding | title = Bulgaria merges energy firms in 4B euro holding | publisher = The Sofia Echo | date = 2008-09-19 | accessdate = 2009-11-16}} </ref> Bulgartransgaz was created on 15 January 2007 in [[Sofia]]. In November 2009, the Bulgarian Government decided to list the company at the [[Bulgarian Stock Exchange - Sofia]].<ref name=sofia111109> {{cite news | url = http://www.sofiaecho.com/2009/11/11/814456_bulgaria-to-list-up-to-15-per-cent-of-energy-holding-subsidiaries | title = Bulgaria to list up to 15 per cent of energy holding, subsidiaries | publisher = The Sofia Echo | date = 2009-11-11 | accessdate = 2009-11-16}} </ref>
